#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:51
#, no-c-format
msgid "Introduction"
msgstr "Uvod"

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:54
#, no-c-format
msgid "What's &kteatime;?"
msgstr "Kaj je &kteatime;?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kteatime; is a handy timer for steeping tea. No longer will you have to "
"guess at how long it takes for your tea to be ready. Simply select the type "
"of tea you have, and it will alert you when the tea is ready to drink."
msgstr ""
"&kteatime; je priročen časovnik za namakanje čaja. Nič več vam ne bo treba "
"ugibati, koliko časa traja, da je vaš čaj pripravljen. Preprosto izberite "
"vrsto čaja, ki ga imate, in opozorilo vas bo, ko bo čaj pripravljen za pitje."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid "How to Use &kteatime;"
msgstr "Kako uporabljati &kteatime;"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:64
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you start up &kteatime;, it will automatically dock itself in your "
"panel. To access the menu, right click on the docked icon. This will present "
"a list of options which are covered in more detail in the next chapter."
msgstr ""
"Ko zaženete &kteatime;, se samodejno zasidra v vašo ploščo. Za dostop do "
"menija z desno miškino tipko kliknite zasidrano ikono. To bo predstavilo "
"seznam možnosti, ki so podrobneje obravnavane v naslednjem poglavju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:67
#, no-c-format
msgid "Timing Your Tea"
msgstr "Čas za vaš čaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:69
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Upon starting, the panel icon will be that of an tea mug. If you click with "
"the &RMB; on the mug and select your tea, an animated clock visualizing the "
"remaining time is displayed on the icon. After the specified time, the tea "
"will be finished, and a suitable message box will be shown. At this point, "
"you can close the message box by clicking on it. This resets also the timer "
"and the clock on the mug disappears again."
msgstr ""
"Ob zagonu bo ikona plošče v obliki skodelice za čaj. Če kliknete z &RMB; na "
"skodelici in izberite svoj čaj, se na ikoni prikaže animirana ura, ki "
"prikazuje preostali čas. Po določenem času bo čaj končan in prikazano bo "
"ustrezno sporočilo. Na tej točki lahko zaprete okno s sporočilom s klikom "
"nanj. To ponastavi tudi časovnik in ura na skodelici spet izgine."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:71
#, no-c-format
msgid "The timer should only be reset by those who really enjoy tea."
msgstr "Časovnik naj ponastavijo samo tisti, ki resnično uživajo v čaju."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:77
#, no-c-format
msgid "Menu Options"
msgstr "Možnosti menija"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:79
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The following section describes the menu options that are available in "
"&kteatime;."
msgstr ""
"Naslednji razdelek opisuje možnosti menija, ki so na voljo v &kteatime;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:82
#, no-c-format
msgid "Select Your Tea"
msgstr "Izberite svoj čaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:84
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking on the icon with the &RMB; will bring up a menu. At the top of the "
"menu there are four menu items. Here, you can select what kind of tea you "
"are preparing to drink. There are: <guimenuitem>Black Tea</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Fruit Tea</guimenuitem>, "
"and <guimenuitem>Green Tea</guimenuitem>. These teas are preconfigured with "
"a default time. Many people have complained that the times are not correct. "
"Please be aware that the amount of time it takes to steep a cup of tea is "
"based on personal preference. The times chosen are approximations. If you "
"read on, you will learn how to change or delete these predefined times and "
"to set your own time. A quick-and-easy way to set a custom time is to choose "
"<guimenuitem>Custom...</guimenuitem> from the menu."
msgstr ""
"S klikom na ikono z &RMB; bo prikazal meni. Na vrhu menija so štirje "
"elementi menija. Tukaj lahko izberete, kakšen čaj želite piti. Obstajajo: "
"<guimenuitem>črni čaj</guimenuitem>, <guimenuitem>Earl Grey</guimenuitem>, "
"<guimenuitem>sadni čaj</guimenuitem> in <guimenuitem>zeleni čaj</"
"guimenuitem>. Ti čaji so vnaprej konfigurirani s privzetim časom. Mnogi "
"ljudje so se pritoževali, da časi niso pravi. Upoštevajte, da je čas, "
"potreben za namakanje skodelice čaja, odvisen od osebnih želja. Izbrani časi "
"so približni. Če boste brali naprej, se boste naučili, kako spremeniti ali "
"izbrisati te vnaprej določene ure in nastaviti svoj čas. Hiter in enostaven "
"način za nastavitev časa po meri je, da v meniju izberete <guimenuitem>Po "
"meri ...</guimenuitem>."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:86
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Clicking <guimenuitem>Configure Notifications...</guimenuitem> brings up the "
"&kde; Notification Settings for &kteatime;."
msgstr ""
"Če kliknete <guimenuitem>Konfiguriraj obvestila ...</guimenuitem>, se "
"prikaže &kde; Nastavitve obvestil za &kteatime;."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:91
#, no-c-format
msgid "Start the Tea Timer"
msgstr "Zaženite časovnik za čaj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:93
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"To start the tea timer select a tea from the context menu. As confirmation "
"that you have indeed started the timer, a clock visualizing the remaining "
"time is displayed in the panel icon."
msgstr ""
"Če želite zagnati časovnik za čaj, izberite čaj v kontekstnem meniju. Kot "
"potrditev, da ste res zagnali časovnik, se na ikoni plošče prikaže ura, ki "
"prikazuje preostali čas."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:97
#, no-c-format
msgid "Configure"
msgstr "Konfiguriraj"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:99
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"This menu item opens up the configuration dialog box. A screenshot is shown "
"below:"
msgstr ""
"Ta element menija odpre pogovorno okno za konfiguracijo. Posnetek zaslona je "
"prikazan spodaj:"

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: index.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid "<screeninfo>The &kteatime; configuration dialog box.</screeninfo>"
msgstr "<screeninfo>&kteatime; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: index.docbook:105
#, no-c-format
msgid "<phrase>The &kteatime; configuration dialog box.</phrase>"
msgstr "<phrase>&kteatime; konfiguracijsko pogovorno okno.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:110
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"As shown in the picture, you may add new entries for other tea or change "
"names, times and the order of existing entries. This is useful if you are "
"brewing a cup of tea that is not on the list or if you do not agree with the "
"predefined times. To edit one entry, mark it in the <guilabel>Tea List</"
"guilabel> on the left and change the values in the <guilabel>Tea Properties</"
"guilabel> on the right."
msgstr ""
"Kot je prikazano na sliki, lahko dodate nove vnose za druge čaje ali "
"spremenite imena, ure in vrstni red obstoječih vnosov. To je uporabno, če "
"kuhate skodelico čaja, ki ni na seznamu, ali če se ne strinjate z vnaprej "
"določenimi časi. Če želite urediti en vnos, ga označite v <guilabel>Seznamu "
"čajev</guilabel> na levi in spremenite vrednosti v <guilabel>Lastnostih "
"čaja</guilabel> na desni."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The box below is the <guilabel>Action</guilabel> field. Here you can define "
"an action that will be executed when the time is up. If <guilabel>Popup</"
"guilabel> is selected, a message box will appear alerting you to the fact "
"that your tea is ready."
msgstr ""
"Spodnje polje je polje <guilabel>Dejanje</guilabel>. Tukaj lahko določite "
"dejanje, ki bo izvedeno, ko čas poteče. Če izberete <guilabel>Pojavno okno</"
"guilabel>, se prikaže okno s sporočilom, ki vas opozori, da je vaš čaj "
"pripravljen."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you enable the check box labeled <guilabel>Visualize progress in icon "
"tray</guilabel>, the progress will be shown as a little animated clock "
"inside the icon."
msgstr ""
"Če omogočite potrditveno polje z oznako <guilabel>Vizualiziraj napredek v "
"vrstici z ikonami</guilabel>, bo napredek prikazan kot majhna animirana ura "
"znotraj ikone."

